metadata.name: PULSE
metadata.description:
Wet In Desires is a nude photography project I discovered the human body once again in a creative way. I sought the essence of sexual desire in human body and gestures during the creative process.  
Our sexual attention can easily triggered by physical appearance. Also gestures may be really attracting for us too. I focused on these 2 visual aspect and benefited by long exposure, double exposure on camera techniques to create a ''desire moment'' effect in photograph. 'Colored Water' and 'Light' represent the space conquered by desires.

Model: Samet Karabay
